ComicInfo.Title: Runequest
ComicInfo.Summary: Runequest: Thor reveals his secret identity to Kincaid to try to convince him that he had nothing to do with the death of Jane Foster. He takes Kincaid and Sif to the home planet of Kamo Tharnn in search of the Runestaff in hopes that it can return Jane to life.
